	<li><a href="#How we can make changes to this policy">How we can make changes to this policy</a></li>
	<li><a href="#Where and how to ask questions or contact us about this policy">Where and how to ask questions or contact us about this policy</a></li>
</ul>
<p>If you are under 16, you must inform a parent or guardian about our privacy policy to obtain their agreement to the privacy policy before registering, subscribing or placing an order with us. </p>

