<p>If you require further information about our privacy policy, please go to the help section of our websites where <a href="/Help/FrequentlyAskedQuestions/en?lang=en">frequently asked questions (FAQ's)</a> are answered. We welcome your questions, comments and requests about this privacy policy. If you require more information, please contact our privacy officer at <a href="mailto:query.dpo@ynap.com">query.dpo@ynap.com</a></p>
